{
  "texts": [
    "The Chinese corpus was used by [32] to generate a summary.",
    "[33] described a neural network that uses a distraction strategy to allow users to focus on different input parts.",
    "A semantic relevance-based neural network was used by [34] to create semantically important summaries of Chinese data.",
    "Finally, [35] used a bidirectional LSTM encoder to generate an extracted summary.",
    "[36] Graph-based techniques used supervised and unsupervised learning schemes to create extractive single-document summaries."
  ]
}